epresentative of when the compile string was propagated rather than when the fixed string will compile. This will remedy the issue of new compiles constantly occuring as well as an issue with the QuickForm displaying print groups.\n\nTesting Instructions\nTo test, view an affected print group. After the code has been run, the print group should display based on the compile string rather than based on other logic.\n\nSpecial Notes\n\nInstallation\nRequires an Outage? No','Print group displaying extra data from original quickform input.','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Test Comment NCF',NULL),(380,2426302,1,1,NULL,1301,NULL,NULL,'KPHC NCAL - PROD Update HB RCSI Metrics with version 13 report parameters',NULL,'2395957',NULL,'Tanya Appel',NULL,NULL,'RSLT','Clo','RC','N',NULL,NULL,'r',NULL,NULL,'A','A',NULL,'SR',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'L','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'S','N','N','N','M','N','N',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2008-03-28 21:00:00','2008-03-24 09:08:13',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2008-04-17 13:24:00',NULL,'A','RESLUTTC','KPHC CN RESOLUTE TECH','Maintenance','Application Services','KPHC Billing (Resolute)',NULL,NULL,' ',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Y',NULL,'N','N','N',NULL,'N',NULL,'A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,563,593,563,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1900-01-01 00:00:00','2008-03-27 00:00:00','2008-03-27 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,138,101,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2008-03-24 09:33:00','2008-03-27 05:45:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','Changes are made on the Shadow Servers.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'KPHC NCAL - PROD Update HB RCSI Metrics with version 13 report parameters','To correct a RCSI reporting data blip related to the soft capitation routines used in the regions.','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Test Comment NCF',NULL),(381,2429140,1,1,NULL,1303,NULL,NULL,'KPHC NCAL HB Insurance - Small Balance Write-Off-Credit-SAA',NULL,'2332671',NULL,