 WQs\nSP07--Turn off AUTO REMOVE COMPLETED setting for four WQs and rebuild history in these WQs for all six instances.\n\nSR Action Requested\n\n1.  Please turn off \"AUTO REMOVE COMPLETED?\" setting for the following four WQs for all NCAL instances (refer to attached Credit WQ Maintenance Setup Screen.jpg screen):\n\na.  ASU MANUAL CREDIT CARD ADJUSTMENT REQUEST FROM LBO\nb.  ASU MANUAL REFUND REQUEST-CASH & CHECK\nc.  ASU MANUAL-INSURANCE CREDIT BALANCE (1056 & 1027)\nd.  ASU MANUAL-REFUND REQUEST FROM UNDISTRIBUTED\n\nAnd any other manual Credit WQs active in PROD. \n\n2.  Ask Epic (Ryan Gonzales) to rebuild history in these Credit WQs going back to the implementation date for the NCAL Spring07 Upgrade (Midnight, 3/15/08).\n\nActually, he may get us reports, but that is it.  This will not be anything other than a user re-populating the WQs.  That is not part of IT change control.  \n\nBACKGROUND & STATEMENT OF PROBLEM\n\nUnder Spring06, CBO used the four manual credit WQs listed above to process refund requests for NCAL and SCAL.  These WQs were created to hold all manual credits regardless whether the credit is still outstanding, has already been matched to a payment or has a zero balance.  These credits would go into these WQ regardless whether they were distributed or undistributed.\n\nUnder Spring06, there was a bug that allowed the credits with a zero balance to stay in these WQs.  After the Spring07 upgrade, that bug was fixed so any credits with a zero balance autocompleted.\n\nCBO business needs to track all manual credits and wants to control what leaves these CR Manual WQs.  They would like history to be restored for all Manual Credit WQs going back to just before the Spring07 upgrade (Midnight, 3/15/08) and to allow CBO to select which transactions should fall out of these WQ.\n\nPer Ryan Gonzales recommendation, we need to TURN OFF the AUTO REMOVE COMPLETED setting under Credit WQ Maintenance  for','The refund process using Manual Credit WQs does not function as designed since the upgrade.  We need to remove a setting so the process can work as designed. ','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Test Comment NCF',NULL),(394,2422918,1,1,NULL,1300,NULL,NULL,'KPHC NCAL Prod Update EAP for Alt ID NCAL 07-067',NULL,'2177299',NULL,'Audrey Juanis',NULL,NULL,'RSLT','Clo','RC','N',NULL,NULL,'r',NULL,NULL,'A','A',NULL,'SR',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'L','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'S','N','N','N','L','N','N',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2008-03-28 11:01:00','2008-03-21 09:17:12',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2008-03-31 08:50:41',NULL,'A','RESLUTTC','KPHC CN RESOLUTE TECH','Maintenance','Application Services','KPHC Billing (Resolute)',NULL,NULL,' ',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Y',NULL,'N','N','N',NULL,'N',NULL,'A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,576,759,576,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1900-01-01 00:00:00','2008-03-27 00:00:00','2008-03-27 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,174,101,174,0,NULL,'2008-03-27 08:28:00','2008-03-27 05:39:00','2008-03-27 08:55:00',NULL,NULL,'P',NULL,'',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'KPHC  NCAL Prod Update EAP for Alt ID NCAL 07-067','Resolute hopital billing-manually update two EAP codes, 211303 and 219837, with alt id 2009, 2010,with eff from date 1/1/2004.','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Test Comment NCF',NULL),(396,2424765,1,1,NULL,1297,NULL,NULL,'KPHC NCAL HB Acct WQs Setup for HOV Depts: HAY-OCTH & STR-PULH',NULL,'3294464',NULL,'Toni Ying',NULL,NULL,'RSLT','Clo','RC','N',NULL,NULL,'r',NULL,NULL,'A','A',NULL,'SR',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'L','EM',NULL,NULL,NULL,'S','N','N','N','M','N','N',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2008-03-27 19:00:00','2008-03-21 14:50:20',NULL,NULL,'SR3294464',NULL,'2008-03-31 08:50:42',NULL,'A','RESLUTTC','KPHC CN RESOLUTE TECH','Workqueues','Application Services','KPHC Billing (Resolute)',NULL,NULL,' 3.00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Y',NULL,'N','N','N',NULL,'N