\nThanks,\n\nRaven R Moore, CPC\n\nRevenue Capture Training Team\nResolute Training Lead\n2101 Webster St, 9th Floor, 93W28\nOakland, CA 94612\n\"','To support Business Decision to bill for DHMO PB encounters during go live of AMB-LAB-RAD full charge capture.\n\nModify patient WQs for DHMO ECL Remediation-Please modify the Patient WQs so that they only include billable encounters. Please see attachment for list of billable departments.','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Test Comment NCF',NULL),(573,2546999,1,1,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,'#KPHC NCAL PROD - 0416-AP-TD24768-E755264-Spr07May12NS.tar.Z',NULL,'24768',NULL,'Teresa Minchew',NULL,NULL,'RSLT','Clo','RC','N',NULL,NULL,'r',NULL,NULL,'A','A',NULL,'TD',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'L','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'C','N','N','N','M','N','N',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2008-05-21 05:00:00','2008-05-05 16:56:49',NULL,'2008-05-21 05:00:00',NULL,NULL,'2008-05-21 03:31:03',NULL,'AR','EEAPIPLN','EE API PLANNING CN','Code/Config Install - CN','End User Applications','KPHC Epic Environment',NULL,NULL,' ',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Y',NULL,'N','Y','N',NULL,'N',NULL,'N',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,699,277,699,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2008-05-06 00:00:00','2008-05-08 00:00:00','2008-05-08 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,143,140,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2008-05-06 04:02:00','2008-05-08 03:07:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','NCF Approval:  5/6/08','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'KPHC NCAL PROD - 0416-AP-TD24768-E755264-Spr07May12NS.tar.Z\n\nDESCRIPTION: Updates patient MRN information during a cross-deployment merge so that outbound transactions to Ingenix send the right patient MRN for billing updates.\n\n5.	Requires an Outage (Y/N)? Yes\na.	What is affected (application and specific functionality): Identity/EMPI Patient Merges\nb.	Minimum outage required (list any process/queues that could be shutdown without bringing the environment to run level 1 to safely install this c