unt.  It just straightens the buckets out (so they are all $0 buckets), and returns the account from bad debt (if it was in bad debt), all of which are things an end user is not able to do on a combined account.\n\nHistorically, this utility ran twice via Epic Systems, however, a KPHC build is not available until Spring 08, which is scheduled for Production in 2009, so we need to schedule with KP-IT API to run on a montly basis. \n\n1) To remedy backlog, please schedule a One Time run for the bulk with API\n2) Then, run monthly using batch scheduler on the same frequency as the Soft Capitation, which is each Sunday and the last day of each month.  Please schedule to run prior to the Soft Capitation system action.\n3) Run until such a date that either Spring 08 ensures 100% remedy with no residual, late discovery is null, or Finance/Business approves of termination by submitted an approved SR to tech.  \n\nApproved by Finance Eric Lindquist, and Tim McDermott, PBS OPS','Clean up imbalance in buckets for Combimned accounts','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Test Comment NCF',NULL),(940,2857910,1,1,NULL,400,NULL,NULL,'KPHC NCAL PROD:  Add ED Confirmation record to Transfer (400)',NULL,'3682999',NULL,'Audrey Carstensen/Ryan Lambert',NULL,NULL,'ADT','Clo','RC','Y',NULL,NULL,'r',NULL,NULL,'A','A',NULL,'HD',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'L','EM',NULL,NULL,NULL,'S','N','N','N','M','N','N',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2008-09-09 21:00:00','2008-08-22 16:13:53',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2008-09-11 05:34:16',NULL,'A','ADTTECH','KPHC CN ADT TECH','Error or Warning','End User Applications','KPHC Admit Discharge Transfer (ADT)',NULL,NULL,' ',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Y',NULL,'N','Y','N',NULL,'N',NULL,'A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,751,940,751,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2008-09-09 00:00:00','2008-08-28 00:00:00','2008-09-09 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,150,97,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2008-08-27 04:33:00','2008-09-09 08:30:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL