*+Current set up:\n\n12 pm :   the Prof Billing diamond ftp job runs and sends one or more PB files to the mainframe (will also send HB files if available)..\n\n12:10 pm:  the Hosp Billing diamond ftp job runs and sends one or more HB files to the mainframe (will also send PB files if there are any there).\n\nNote:   there is separate \"job\" dependencies on the two jobs above.  One is dependent on the PB extract and the other dependent on the HB extract.  So if those extract jobs were to run late, then the ftp jobs would not run until their respective dependent job finished.\n\n\n*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*+Proposed changes.\n\n12 pm :  the Prof Billing diamond job will run and will only process PB files  (HB files will be removed).\n1 pm:    the Hosp Billing diamond job will run and will only process HB files  (PB files will be removed).\n\nAn FTP command will be added to the above jobs that \"cleans\" any failed ftp files, so partial files cannot be created on the mainframe (this is extra precaution from Dino).\n\n3 pm -   EDI will run their \"time dependent\" job   (note:  this is proposed EDI change that not dependent on our changes).\n\nNote:  regardless of EDI changes, our changes will fix the problem of dupes and missing files, because the jobs will be spread out timewise and\n            will only be processing PB or HB files exclusively.','This is to rectify sending duplicate files to Diamond.  This problem was encountered by SCAL and NCAL is making the same change to avoid this issue in the future.','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Test Comment NCF',NULL),(1362,3281497,1,1,NULL,1907,NULL,NULL,'KPHC NCAL PROD Update venture price contracts with new prices and some new codes.',NULL,'3261746',NULL,'Matt Nunes',NULL,NULL,'RSLT','Clo','RC','N',NULL,NULL,'R',NULL,NULL,'A','A',NULL,'SR',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'L','EM',NULL,NULL,NULL,'S','N','N','N','L','N','N',NULL,NULL,'2009-01-26 07:00:00','2009-01-26 17:00:00','2009-01-19 11:5