00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'KPHC NCAL PROD-Interface Improvement Project KPFS/KPHC - Rules to support Common Edits for patient demographics\n\nNew Rules for Common Edits to support the Interface Improvement Project.  These rules will stop users from editing patient demographics in such a way that the message will fail in KPFS.\n\nNew rules to prevent the use of special characters in Name\n                 to prevent certain SSN configurations\n                 to prevent entering Non-Numeric phone number\n                 to prevent a space as first character in an address.','New Rules for Common Edits to support the Interface Improvement Project.','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Test Comment NCF',NULL),(1364,3287826,1,1,NULL,206,NULL,NULL,'KPHC NCAL - PROD Documents change status list for AOB and Financial Responsibility',NULL,'3283367',NULL,'Cindy Bates',NULL,NULL,'PRLD','Clo','RC','N',NULL,NULL,'R',NULL,NULL,'A','A',NULL,'SR',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'L','CM',NULL,NULL,NULL,'S','N','N','N','L','N','N',NULL,NULL,'2009-02-21 02:00:00','2009-02-21 06:00:00','2009-01-20 16:11:56',NULL,'2009-02-21 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,'2009-02-23 05:33:17',NULL,'A','PRELUDE','KPHC CN PRELUDE TECH','Documents','End User Applications','KPHC Benefits/Accts/Coverages (Prelude)',NULL,NULL,' ','Approval',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Y',NULL,'N','N','N',NULL,'N',NULL,'A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,871,1205,871,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1900-01-01 00:00:00','2009-01-29 00:00:00','2009-01-29 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,162,133,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2009-01-20 04:16:00','2009-01-29 03:23:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'KPHC NCAL - PROD Documents change status list for AOB and Financial Responsibility\n\nKPHC NCAL - Documents change status list for AOB and Financial Responsibility\n\nCurrently all status values are available for these documents.  This request is to limit the list to\n\nReceived\nNot Received\nPatient Refused\n\nThere will be a FOOI initiative to train front office to begin giving a new form to patients to match the business requirements below.  This is a combined AOB and Notice of Financial responsibility.   Although it physically is one form, it is a combination form  and RDs will have to enter both forms to document the signature on the form.  To simplify that process, the long list of statuses will be limited to the 3 listed above.\n\nThe configuration change complexity and level of testing required is low, and the urgency to get this configured quickly is high.  February release date is targeted.\n\nIn addition, ADT and ED were polled by business regarding this change and they responded that they are not impacted.\n\nBusiness requirements:\n\nAOB Requirements:\nRequired for nonmembers and members whenever KP intends to bill a government or commercial payor only.  This would therefore exclude TPL, WC, and Corporate financial classes.\nExcludes out-of-region members.  (Policy stipulates only that they are a member of a KFHP plan).\nPer TPMG leadership decision, SF patients are treated as KP members.\n\nAOB Language:\nASSIGNMENT OF BENEFITS:  The undersigned, whether signing as a patient or personal representative of the patient, authorizes direct payment to the hospital and the patientâ€™s health care providers of any health care coverage benefits otherwise payable to or on behalf of the patient for these outpatient services. Health care coverage benefits include Medicare, Medi-Cal, other governmental health care program benefits or commercial payors. \n\nNFR Clarification:\nCollected for all nonmembers, regardless if they are self-pay.\nIncludes collecting for patients who claim membership','See Summary for details','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Test Comment NCF',NULL),(1365,3269816,1,1,NULL,