s {xx]\n2.  Add an action that will automatically write off the insurance balance to AR Code 3001, as it qualifies for the WQ.\n3.  See WQ form attached, for details and SPAR \n4.  See HAR example attached in work doc.  \n\n\nApproved by Margarita Suarez, DPST','Create a new HB Account WQ, to capture HARs that have DHMO Primary, that have been billed, and have an outstanding insurnace balance to be billed to the secondary coverage.  Then create a system action to write the secondary balance off','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Test Comment NCF',NULL),(1530,2953426,1,1,NULL,1662,NULL,NULL,'KPHC NC PROD RCSI:  Implement SpaceTrax  Charge Capture',NULL,'2916809',NULL,'Adele Fingerman',NULL,NULL,'RSLT','Clo','RC','N',NULL,NULL,'R',NULL,NULL,'A','A',NULL,'SR',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'L','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'S','N','N','N','L','N','N',NULL,NULL,'2009-04-01 08:00:00','2009-04-15 16:00:00','2008-09-24 17:30:54',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2009-05-11 05:29:58',NULL,'A','RESLUTTC','KPHC CN RESOLUTE TECH','Configuration Change','End User Applications','KPHC Billing (Resolute)',NULL,NULL,' ','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Y',NULL,'N','Y','N',NULL,'N',NULL,'N',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,563,42,570,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2009-03-23 00:00:00','2009-03-19 00:00:00','2009-03-23 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,138,140,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2009-03-16 10:11:00','2009-03-24 09:54:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','3/23/09:  Received NCF approval.','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'KPHC NC PROD RCSI:  Implement SpaceTrax Charge Capture. Build Charge Router tasks and WQ changes related to SpaceTrax charge capture.','Part of RCSI full charge capture project.','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Test Comment NCF',NULL),(1531,3244900,1,1,NULL,220,NULL,NULL,'KPHC NCAL PROD - Cadence - Turn on the Orders Tab in the LAB/RAD OF Facilities. CVA [MAN/STK/MOD/TRA]  (Out of Cyle