te the need for administration staff phone calls and manual data entry follow-up.\n\nHaving current and accurate coverage information improves our ability to submit claims for reimbursement before invoicing the patient directly. \n','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Test Comment NCF',NULL),(1560,3165015,1,1,NULL,231,NULL,NULL,'KPHC CN PROD - NCAL NEVI Phase II (Integrated Solution) - Edit Service Area System Defs in Prelude.',NULL,'2265451',NULL,'John Haligheri',NULL,NULL,'PRLD','Clo','RC','Y',NULL,NULL,'R',NULL,NULL,'A','A',NULL,'SR',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'L','TR',NULL,NULL,NULL,'S','N','N','N','L','Y','N',NULL,NULL,'2009-04-08 03:00:00','2009-04-08 06:00:00','2008-12-04 13:30:02',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2009-04-14 05:31:22',NULL,'A','PRELUDE','KPHC CN PRELUDE TECH','Regional - Configuration Change','End User Applications','KPHC Benefits/Accts/Coverages (Prelude)',NULL,NULL,' ','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Y',NULL,'N','Y','N',NULL,'N',NULL,'N',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,936,684,936,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2009-03-23 00:00:00','2009-03-19 00:00:00','2009-03-23 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,163,140,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2009-03-18 11:34:00','2009-03-24 10:39:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','3/23/09:  Received NCF approval. ','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'KPHC CN PROD - NCAL NEVI Phase II (Integrated Solution) - Edit Service Area System Defs and all associated functionality within to enable Electronic Eligibility in Prelude.','Although many of the patients seen at KP NCAL\'s facilities are health plan members with Kaiser Permanente Health Plan or Kaiser Permanente Insurance Corp., some are either non-members or have coverage with other health plans or health plan insurers.  Currently, NCAL KP staffs often spend a considerable amount of time researching and making follow-up calls at significant cost to obtain and verify insurance information. \n\nLeveraging on those payers able