alue that has the SSN as part of the value (i.e., Medicare Numbers), this code is needed ASAP.\n\n\nCommunication has been given to the Prelude Reps.  The recommendation is to take this Ad Hoc along with Ad Hoc 4558 (Masked data stored instead of actual value for Subscriber ID and Member ID field (CVG 220 & 315)) as soon as possible.\n\n\nRegions are strongly urged to install this code item as the earliest possible opportunity.','To be hipaa compliant','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Test Comment NCF',NULL),(1573,3476605,1,1,NULL,2049,NULL,NULL,'KPHC NCAL PROD-Getting wrong facilities appearing in workque 1088',NULL,'4312398',NULL,'None required',NULL,NULL,'RSLT','Clo','RC','N',NULL,NULL,'R',NULL,NULL,'A','A',NULL,'HD',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'L','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'S','N','N','N','L','N','N',NULL,NULL,'2009-03-20 14:00:00','2009-03-20 14:30:00','2009-03-20 13:01:47','2009-03-20 14:10:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2009-03-24 12:43:20',NULL,'A','HIMTECH','KPHC CN HIM CODING TECH','Workqueues','End User Applications','KPHC Billing (Resolute)',NULL,NULL,' ','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'A',NULL,'N','N','N',NULL,'N',NULL,'A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,581,1266,581,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1900-01-01 00:00:00','2009-03-26 00:00:00','2009-03-26 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,157,140,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2009-03-24 12:36:00','2009-03-26 03:14:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','Change authorized for 3/20/09 (Tom Cardella).  Change required as end user had affected WQ rule','Prod RFC only.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'KPHC-Getting wrong facilities appearing in workque 1088','Insure that the proper accounts are falling into the WQ','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Test Comment NCF',NULL),(1574,3408266,1,1,NULL,221,NULL,NULL,'KPHC NCAL PROD:  create new VT PNGS 9418',NULL,'3388821',NULL,'Rod Ocmond',NULL,NULL,'CAD','Clo','RC','Y',NULL,NULL,'R',NULL,NUL