ould alert the RD that she has canceled the check in and will \nneed to check it in again.  \n\nWould suggest that the message ask you if you really want to cancel the check in \nand give you the option of Not Canceling - this may be a better enhancement\n\nBenefit Of Change:	It would be less likely that a Pt.s appt. is cancelled by mistake.\n\nImpact/Risk of\nNot Making Change:   Dr. does not see on his schedule that a pt. has arrived for a visit.\n\nAlternative Options \nor Work-Around:           Reschedule the pt.s appt. if the error occurs. \n\n##','Patient appointments are being cancelled by mistake','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Test Comment NCF',NULL),(1638,3523927,1,1,NULL,245,NULL,NULL,'KPHC NCAL PROD- Inactivate the Delete button on documents table for outpatient users',NULL,'3368155',NULL,'Udipi Rajagopal ',NULL,NULL,'PRLD','Clo','RC','N',NULL,NULL,'R',NULL,NULL,'A','A',NULL,'SR',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'L','CM',NULL,NULL,NULL,'S','N','N','N','L','N','N',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2009-05-13 06:00:00','2009-04-06 11:54:48',NULL,'2009-05-13 06:00:00',NULL,NULL,'2009-05-19 08:10:56',NULL,'A','PRELUDE','KPHC CN PRELUDE TECH','Regional - Configuration Change','End User Applications','KPHC Benefits/Accts/Coverages (Prelude)',NULL,NULL,' ','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Y',NULL,'N','N','N',NULL,'N',NULL,'A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,871,867,871,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1900-01-01 00:00:00','2009-04-23 00:00:00','2009-04-23 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,162,140,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2009-04-21 09:29:00','2009-04-23 03:33:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'KPHC NCAL - Inactivate the Delete button on documents table for outpatient users.\n\nThis is a shared security setting - a similar setting done for ADT users recently.  This will prevent the alteration of patient records.\n\nShared Security Classes\n\nNCAL SHARED USER [100010]  \n\nNCAL SHARED USER