erk still needs to follow their workflow of using Cadence to check in.\n\nWe are requesting to allow the registration clerks to book an appointment at the same time as the surgery.\n\nBusiness Requirements:\n\nIn the Cadence Security Classes for Registration Clerks - Please set Overlap with Cases - Yes\n\nIn the Cadence System definitions - Schedule section - Set Allow overlap with cases? - Yes\n\nPlease identify the correct Cadence Front Office ECLs.\n\nNCAL_ES_RECEPTION\nNCAL_ES_SCHEDULER\nNCAL_ES_MA/RD\nNCAL_ES_CLINICIAN\nNCAL_ES_MA/LVN/RN\nNCAL_ES_PSY_RECEPTION\n\n\nRequest to build this across the region to support future deployments of ASDs.  Next deployment for ASD would be STR and/or SSF.  The date for SSF is not known at this time.  STR is in July 09.  I will confirm these dates with our project manager.\n\n-Darryl Gill','Allows staff to create surgical cases six weeks in advance of IP2 go live','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Test Comment NCF',NULL),(1744,3678534,1,1,NULL,272,NULL,NULL,'KPHC NC PROD - NCAL EVI Phase II - Batch Modification. (PRODCAM)',NULL,'3654138',NULL,'Production only change ',NULL,NULL,'CAD','Clo','RC','N',NULL,NULL,'R',NULL,NULL,'A','A',NULL,'SR',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'L','EM',NULL,NULL,NULL,'S','N','N','N','L','N','N',NULL,NULL,'2009-06-02 22:00:00','2009-06-02 23:00:00','2009-05-26 13:29:29',NULL,'2009-05-02 22:00:00',NULL,NULL,'2009-06-03 08:16:08',NULL,'A','CADTECH','KPHC CN CADENCE TECH','Regional - Configuration Change','End User Applications','KPHC OP/Check-In (Cadence/HOV)',NULL,NULL,' ','Approval',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'N',NULL,'N','N','N',NULL,'N',NULL,'PO',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,240,1052,240,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1900-01-01 00:00:00','2009-05-28 00:00:00','2009-05-28 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,114,133,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2009-05-26 09:14:00','2009-05-28 03:08:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1243547872ï££Remedy