siness practice in the region.  \n\n\nNote: NCAL Does not use Donor accounts currently.','Enhancement to improve billing operations','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Test Comment NCF',NULL),(1756,3674163,1,1,NULL,256,NULL,NULL,'KPHC NCAL PROD - Modifications to MSPQ launch behavior',NULL,'3387822',NULL,'Mary Sears',NULL,NULL,'PRLD','Clo','RC','N',NULL,NULL,'R',NULL,NULL,'A','A',NULL,'SR',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'L','CM',NULL,NULL,NULL,'S','N','N','N','L','N','N',NULL,NULL,'2009-06-17 02:00:00','2009-06-17 04:00:00','2009-05-22 14:43:26',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2009-06-17 07:05:40',NULL,'A','PRELUDE','KPHC CN PRELUDE TECH','Regional - Configuration Change','End User Applications','KPHC Benefits/Accts/Coverages (Prelude)',NULL,NULL,' ','Approval',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'N',NULL,'N','N','N',NULL,'N',NULL,'A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,801,1205,801,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1900-01-01 00:00:00','2009-05-28 00:00:00','2009-05-28 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,164,133,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2009-05-27 10:25:00','2009-05-28 03:40:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1244742490ï££Remedy Application Serviceï££Approval process complete. Christopher B Dunham, has been notified approvalï£¢','','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Modifications to MSPQ launch behavior\n\nBased on review of MSPQ from outside legal counsel, the business requirements for system support have changed.\n\nCadence:\nDiscontinue having MSPQ message \"Access to the MSPQ is not necessary at this time.  Do you want to open it anyway?  yes or no.\"  display when the MSPQ has already been completed.\nThe MSPQ is still required once annually (rolling calendar) and should automatically open the form on the next encounter when the rolling calendar year ends.\nThe MSPQ form should open as soon as a Medicare FFS coverage is created, or at least at some point during that same encounter.\nThe MSPQ form should still open for every encounter until all data fields are completed.\nDiscontinue prompting for MSPQ completion if visit type=Telephone Visit (27)\nNumber the questions in the MSPQ form in KPHC to match the laminated form, 1-13.  (See attached).\n\n\nED ADT:\nThe MSPQ is still required for every ED encounter\nAdd a warning message to prompt to open the MSPQ.  (At least 1 facility reports that no prompt appears in KPHC.)\nThe MSPQ form should open as soon as a Medicare FFS coverage is created or at least at some point during that same encounter.\nNumber the questions in the MSPQ form in KPHC to match the laminated form, 1-13.  (See attached).\n\nNOTE:  ED portion assigned to ADT via SR  3463367\n\n\nHOV- lets hold on this.  Id like to get in writing confirmation from Rev Cycle that they agree to this (I currently only have a verbal agreement for this process):\nChange HOV configuration to copy previous MSPQ answers from MOB or ED encounters.  An MSPQ record is still required for every HOV encounter and every 90 days for recurring services.\nDiscontinue the MSP form opening and all MSP prompts in HOV.','To improve MSPQ completion rates','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Test Comment NCF',NULL),(1757,3678889,1,1,NULL,275,NULL,NULL,'KPHC NCAL - Change HIPAA Document status options to:  Received, Not Received, Patient Refused',NULL,'3387902',NULL,'Nguyen,Cj',NULL,NULL,'PRLD','Clo','RC','N',NULL,NULL,'R',NULL,NULL,'A','A',NULL,'SR',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'L','EM',NULL,NULL,NULL,'S','N','N','N','L','Y','N',NULL,NULL,'2009-06-16 22:00:00','2009-06-17 06:00:00','2009-05-26 14:14:29',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2009-06-17 07:05:40',NULL,'A','PRELUDE','KPHC CN PRELUDE TECH','Documents','End User Applications','KPHC Benefits/Accts/Coverages (Prelude)',NULL,NULL,' ','Owner Action',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Y',NULL,'N','N','N',NULL,'N',NULL,'A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,552,1205,552,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1900-01-01 00:00:00','2009-05-28 00:00:00','2009-0