sheet for workflow and impacted WQs\n\nPlease contact Rod Dayley or Jennifer J Chandler with any questions','Supports KPHP directive to not balance bill CSI/SF members when they have dual KP Coverage',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Test Comment NCF',NULL),(1860,3776004,1,1,NULL,291,NULL,NULL,'KPHC NC PROD - NCAL EVI Phase II - Batch Activation (PRODGGM) and Security Class Configuration',NULL,'3654250',NULL,'PRODUCTION ONLY',NULL,NULL,'CAD','Clo','RC','N',NULL,NULL,'R',NULL,NULL,'A','A',NULL,'SR',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'L','TR',NULL,NULL,NULL,'S','N','N','N','L','N','N',NULL,NULL,'2009-06-30 20:00:00','2009-06-30 22:01:00','2009-06-23 15:32:29',NULL,'2009-06-30 22:00:00',NULL,NULL,'2009-07-02 06:17:09',NULL,'A','CADTECH','KPHC CN CADENCE TECH','Regional - Configuration Change','End User Applications','KPHC OP/Check-In (Cadence/HOV)',NULL,NULL,' ','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'A',NULL,'N','N','N',NULL,'N',NULL,'PO',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,936,1052,240,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1900-01-01 00:00:00','2009-06-25 00:00:00','2009-06-25 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,114,140,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2009-06-23 08:23:00','2009-06-25 02:44:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1245972669ï££Remedy Application Serviceï££Approval process complete. Matthew T Eager, has been notified approvalï£¢','','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'KPHC NC PROD - NCAL EVI Phase II - Batch Activation (PRODGGM) and Security Class Configuration\nChange is specific only to PRODGGM.\n\nThis SR documents the ff. tasks in support of the EVI implementation in the Centracl Valley instance:\n1.) Activate, Schedule Batch Job: NC_PRE_1110005_FUTURE_APPTS_CVG_VERIFICATION\n2.) Adding security point - 190 - May Use Coverage Eligibility & Toolbar Menu Option 15414 - Verify Information to the following registration security classes:  \n\n\"	NCAL REG ES RD/MA [140202]	\"	NCAL REG ADT FULL ACCESS [140103]\n\"	NCAL REG ES MOCC [1402